					<h2 class="cta__heading">Starting position</h2>
					<p>When the grid is pulsing, select a starting position. Once both players have selected a starting position, a
						player will be chosen at random to go first.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="cta__column--rules-video">
					<video src="/videos/starting-pos.mp4" autoplay muted loop></video>
