				<div class="cta__column--rules-text js-rules-text">
					<h2 class="cta__heading">Roll or dig</h2>
					<p>When it’s your turn, you can choose to either roll or dig. If you choose roll, the die will roll between 1 and
						6. The cells you can move to will then be highlighted. Players can only move in a straight line. Click on the
						cell you want to move to.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="cta__column--rules-video">
					<video src="/videos/warm.mp4" autoplay muted loop></video>
				</div>
